    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this beauty since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and staying on top of every single detail. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next big adventure. You seriously won't find another one this clean! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
