    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, featuring the iconic wide-body silhouette and integrated rear reflector strip. This example is powered by a mid-mounted 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering 320 hp through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The viscous-coupling AWD system ensures optimal torque distribution, while the factory M030 sport suspension and Turbo-spec 'Big Red' monoblock calipers provide surgical turn-in and braking performance. Mechanically peerless, the IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a dual-row ceramic retrofit, and a recent borescope inspection confirmed zero cylinder wall scoring. The finish is flawless, with consistent paint meter readings across all panels. A true driver\u2019s spec with zero deferred maintenance.",
