    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle presents in breathtaking, showroom-fresh condition, finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that remains entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns with factory precision. Inside, the cabin retains that distinct new-car aroma; the premium leather seats show absolutely no bolster wear or creasing, and the high-gloss trim is devoid of even the slightest hairline scratches. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. The engine bay is clinically clean, and the car drives with the tightness and responsiveness of the day it first left the assembly line. It has been meticulously garaged under a breathable cover and serviced exclusively by authorized master technicians, with a complete, documented service history included. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a flawless example that looks, feels, and performs as if it were brand new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
